Application Club.

114
00:07:45,498 --> 00:07:48,168
[MISAKI]
Guess I should've known better.

115
00:07:50,737 --> 00:07:52,573
[YUKIMURA]
Kanou, a little
more to the right!

116
00:07:52,673 --> 00:07:54,675
Oh, the left side is
drooping a little now.

117
00:07:54,775 --> 00:07:57,711
