tomorrow, huh?

119
00:08:00,747 --> 00:08:02,148
Misaki. Please
come take a look.

120
00:08:02,248 --> 00:08:06,920
I'd like to use these...
for our cosplay costumes.

121
00:08:07,020 --> 00:08:09,923
(MISAKI stunned)
[SAKURA] (giggles)
Aren't they great!

122
00:08:10,023 --> 00:08:12,058
[SHIZUKO]
It took a lot of work
to get these prepared.

123
00:08:12,158 --> 00:08:15,195
[GIRL A]
Our teacher said they
looked nice, too.

124
00:08:15,295 --> 00:08:16,963
[SAKURA]
Are they no good, Misaki?

125
00:08:17,063 --> 00:08:21,568
[MISAKI, thinking]
No... This... This could be
exactly what we need!

126
00:08:22,603 --> 00:08:23,770
[MISAKI]
It's all right.

127
00:08:23,870 --> 00:08:25,371
Wear these and do your best!

128
00:08:25,471 --> 00:08:27,508
