214
00:12:26,513 --> 00:12:29,449
(MOB screaming)

215
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:35,255
Well, guess that's that.
Make sure to help out the
sports clubs to the best
of your ability.

216
00:12:35,355 --> 00:12:36,923
'Kay?

217
00:12:40,827 --> 00:12:44,831
W‐wait just a minute! I
couldn't! I CAN'T greet
the visitors!

218
00:12:44,931 --> 00:12:46,700
[GIRL A]
C'mon, don't say that.

219
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:50,370
[GIRL B]
Yeah, come on‐ we have a costume
ready for you and everything!

220
00:12:50,470 --> 00:12:53,039
