and have fun without me!

221
00:12:53,139 --> 00:12:54,941
We couldn't possibly do
something like that.

222
00:12:55,041 --> 00:12:56,877
Yeah, after all, if
it wasn't for you

223
00:12:56,977 --> 00:12:58,845
we never could've gotten
this done. Right?

224
00:12:58,945 --> 00:13:01,548
[SAKURA]
Let's all have fun together!

225
00:13:03,383 --> 00:13:05,552
[GIRL A]
You've helped us out
so much, Kanou.

226
00:13:05,652 --> 00:13:07,954
[GIRL B]
Though you did run away
a lot at first...

227
00:13:08,054 --> 00:13:09,523
[GIRL C]
