228
00:13:09,623 --> 00:13:11,992
all you need to worry about is
setting the tables, Kanou.

229
00:13:12,092 --> 00:13:14,795
[GIRL D]
And if anything happens, we'll
be here to back you up.

230
00:13:14,895 --> 00:13:18,131
See! Look at what a good
time Yukimura's having!

231
00:13:18,231 --> 00:13:19,600
Hm? Gahhhh!

232
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:23,236
