233
00:13:23,336 --> 00:13:28,642
Don't worry, Kanou. We've got
the perfect costume for you‐
you'll LOVE it... (evil giggles)

234
00:13:28,742 --> 00:13:30,944
(KANOU freaking out)

235
00:13:41,688 --> 00:13:43,356
(whistle blowing)

236
00:13:45,358 --> 00:13:47,561
Come on everybody,
let's play soccer!

237
00:13:47,661 --> 00:13:50,997
Be friends
with the ball!

238
00:13:51,097 --> 00:13:54,334
Usui! Come over to
the baseball club next!
[BASEBALL Club, chanting]
Usui, Usui!

239
00:13:56,436 --> 00:13:58,905
[MISAKI] Has everyone been
enjoying themselves so far?
[GIRL A] Yeah!

240
00:13:59,005 --> 00:14:01,575
