is really wonderful,
don't you think?

272
00:15:31,732 --> 00:15:35,301
(thinking) Yeah. Especially
like this... Right?

273
00:15:36,770 --> 00:15:39,606
Well, I'm going to take another
look around, I'll see you guys
later‐

274
00:15:39,706 --> 00:15:42,676
Oh, whoa!
(shock)

275
00:15:48,915 --> 00:15:51,552
Don't you look
cute today, Kanou.

276
00:15:51,652 --> 00:15:54,655
It's not my fault! I
was surrounded by girls
with no way to escape!

277
00:15:54,755 --> 00:15:57,423
Oh really? You sure you're
not enjoying yourself?

278
00:15:57,524 --> 00:16:00,994
YOU'RE WRONG! This
is exactly why I
can't stand girls!

279
00:16:01,094 --> 00:16:02,896
How is this costume "perfect"
for me?

280
00:16:02,996 --> 00:16:05,866
