wishy‐washy?! I don't
understand it!

283
00:16:12,673 --> 00:16:16,009
[KANOU] Just what kind
of creatures are they?!
[MISAKI, thinking] When it comes
to girls, this guy is...

284
00:16:16,109 --> 00:16:19,580
[KANOU]
Women... Women are
just so breakable...

285
00:16:21,047 --> 00:16:26,352
Kanou, seems you can
look us in the eye when
talking now. Heh.
Huh?

286
00:16:26,452 --> 00:16:29,990
These past couple of days you
saw for yourself, didn't you?

287
00:16:30,090 --> 00:16:35,028
[MISAKI]
Do you really think that's true?
Have the girls really been as
weak and fragile as you thought?

288
00:16:35,128 --> 00:16:37,864
Kanou!

289
00:16:37,964 --> 00:16:40,601
You don't have to run
away anymore, Kanou.

290
00:16:45,506 --> 00:16:50,143
This is the first time...
I've ever been around girls
like this.

291
00:16:50,243 --> 00:16:52,679
[BOY] Point!
(KENDO CLUB cheering)

292
00:16:52,779 --> 00:16:54,180
[JR. HIGH BOY] Dammit!
[KENDO CLUB] Don't go looking
down on us high schoolers!

293
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:55,649
Usui! Come to
our club next!

294
00:16:55,749 --> 00:16:56,482
No, ours!

295
00:16:56,583 --> 00:17:03,056
(CLUBS arguing)

296
00:17:03,156 --> 00:17:04,057
(silence)

297
00:17:04,157 --> 00:17:05,125
[USUI]
I've had enough.

298
00:17:05,225 --> 00:17:07,260
(CLUBS stunned)

299
00:17:08,595 --> 00:17:10,196
[BOY]
O... okay...

300
00:17:15,335 --> 00:17:17,437
[GIRL A]
Maybe we should go with Seika.

301
00:17:17,538 --> 00:17:21,474
Huh? A‐are you girls thinking
about enrolling at Seika?!

302
00:17:21,575 --> 00:17:22,342
That's wonderful!

303
00:17:22,442 --> 00:17:24,678
[MISAKI]
So you like it here?!

304
00:17:24,778 --> 00:17:28,048
Yes! Uh, but I... Oh, gosh!

305
00:17:28,148 --> 00:17:29,550
[MISAKI]
Wh‐What is it?

306
00:17:29,650 --> 00:17:32,886
[GIRL A]
The truth is, I'm not
very good with boys.

307
00:17:32,986 --> 00:17:34,721
They're kinda scary.

308
00:17:34,821 --> 00:17:38,058
[GIRL B]
She's only ever been in
all‐girls environments.

309
00:17:38,158 --> 00:17:41,562
[GIRL C]
The only reason she came today
was because we asked her to.

310
00:17:41,662 --> 00:17:44,531
[GIRL A]
There are a lot of boys
at Seika, aren't there?

311
00:17:44,631 --> 00:17:47,267
I wish it was a
girls‐only school...

312
00:17:51,137 --> 00:17:53,473
[YOUNG KANOU]
Dad! What do you mean,
Mom "broke" and went away?

313
00:17:53,574 --> 00:17:58,044
[KANOU'S FATHER]
Soutarou! Women are
more delicate and
fragile than you think!

314
00:17:58,144 --> 00:18:00,113
You gotta
watch how you handle women,

315
00:18:00,213 --> 00:18:01,715
or they'll break on you.

316
00:18:01,815 --> 00:18:03,249
(sobbing)
Mooom!

317
00:18:03,349 --> 00:18:05,952
If they're gonna break,
I'll never go near them again!

318
00:18:06,052 --> 00:18:09,322
[YOUNG KANOU] Girls are scary!
[KANOU] I understand.
I understand now.

319
00:18:09,422 --> 00:18:11,558
[KANOU]
My mom didn't "break"...

320
00:18:11,658 --> 00:18:15,395
She was just sick of the
way my father treated her,
so she left...

321
00:18:15,495 --> 00:18:17,297
I've known... the whole time!

322
00:18:17,397 --> 00:18:18,832
[SAKURA]
Oh, there you are!

323
00:18:18,932 --> 00:18:20,767
Hey, Kanou!

324
00:18:20,867 --> 00:18:22,402
Come here for a minute.

325
00:18:22,503 --> 00:18:26,607
[KANOU] But right now, I'm‐
[SAKURA] It's fine, just
come on!

326
00:18:26,707 --> 00:18:30,343
[KANOU, thinking]
I've known this for
a long time now...

327
00:18:30,443 --> 00:18:32,145
Still, I didn't think
I could go near them.

328
00:18:32,245 --> 00:18:34,347
(YOUNG KANOU crying)

329
00:18:34,447 --> 00:18:35,982
[KANOU] If I got too close...

330
00:18:36,082 --> 00:18:39,520
I thought something painful
would happen, like back then.

331
00:18:39,620 --> 00:18:45,025
Because women are
weak and fragile.

332
00:18:45,125 --> 00:18:49,195
[MISAKI]
Have these girls really been as
weak and fragile as you thought?

333
00:18:53,934 --> 00:18:57,604
Guys are no good, huh? That
does make things pretty tough...

334
00:18:58,471 --> 00:18:59,740
[MISAKI] Okay then.
[GIRLS] Huh?

335
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:01,307
Is THIS guy scary?

336
00:19:01,407 --> 00:19:03,977
[KANOU] Uh...
[GIRL A] Oh! Well...

337
00:19:04,077 --> 00:19:05,812
[MISAKI]
Hey, Bunny Boy!

338
00:19:05,912 --> 00:19:09,315
Show them you're not scary!

339
00:19:09,415 --> 00:19:11,518
[MISAKI] Take a good look.
[KANOU] AH! Huh?

340
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:17,490
You see? He's not scary at all.

341
00:19:22,295 --> 00:19:23,530
Right?

342
00:19:23,630 --> 00:19:25,331
Uh, yeah...

343
00:19:26,733 --> 00:19:29,202
[MISAKI]
You don't have to
run away anymore.

344
00:19:32,338 --> 00:19:34,307
[KANOU] Very well.
[MISAKI] Huh?

345
00:19:34,875 --> 00:19:36,510
(HAPPY)
Ahhh!

346
00:19:39,012 --> 00:19:41,281
I will now cast a magic spell.

347
00:19:42,516 --> 00:19:44,518
Please close your eyes.

348
00:19:47,854 --> 00:19:49,255
Listen to my voice.

349
00:19:49,355 --> 00:19:51,157
From now on you are...

350
00:19:51,257 --> 00:19:54,094
(thinking) I am...
(spoken) ...no longer afraid!

351
00:19:54,194 --> 00:19:55,829
(clap)

352
00:20:05,171 --> 00:20:08,408
(GIRL chuckling)
(GIRLS laughing)

353
00:20:08,509 --> 00:20:11,344
It worked! I don't feel
scared at all! Heh.

354
00:20:12,478 --> 00:20:14,380
[GIRL B] That's
cause it's magic!
[GIRL A] Yeah...

355
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:16,416
[GIRL C] That was cute!
[GIRL B] Mhmmm

356
00:20:16,517 --> 00:20:19,085
[GIRL C] And those bunny
ears are funny!

357
00:20:19,185 --> 00:20:21,822
(courtyard chatter)

358
00:20:21,922 --> 00:20:24,825
Looks like you know some cute
magic tricks, don't you...

359
00:20:24,925 --> 00:20:26,527
...Bunny Boy?

360
00:20:26,627 --> 00:20:28,929
Oh, once you're done with
that, you can head out.

361
00:20:29,029 --> 00:20:31,297
Okay.

362
00:20:31,397 --> 00:20:36,903
[MISAKI]
Kanou, good job today.
As promised, everything
is forgiven.

363
00:20:37,003 --> 00:20:39,372
Be safe on your way home 'kay?

364
00:20:42,108 --> 00:20:43,777
Um, Miss Presi‐!

365
00:20:45,646 --> 00:20:47,013
Huh?

366
00:20:47,981 --> 00:20:49,916
You did a good job, too...

367
00:20:55,889 --> 00:21:00,093
Uh... Thanks for your hard
work, we couldn't have done
it without you.

368
00:21:00,193 --> 00:21:04,364
[MISAKI]
I wonder where we're going... I
wonder if you'll let me down...

369
00:21:04,464 --> 00:21:09,636
I wonder why you won't say
anything... Uh, Usui?
(hitting the ground) Gah!

370
00:21:13,039 --> 00:21:15,642
[USUI]
Feeling satisfied?
With your punishment.

371
00:21:15,742 --> 00:21:17,978
Uh, yeah, that's already
taken care of...

372
00:21:18,078 --> 00:21:22,516
Oh, really? Then maybe you
wouldn't you mind giving
ME a little thanks, too.

373
00:21:22,616 --> 00:21:25,485
You didn't come check on me
once. Man, I'm exhausted.

374
00:21:25,586 --> 00:21:27,721
Well‐ if it wasn't for
you Usui the sports clubs

375
00:21:27,821 --> 00:21:29,923
would've crashed and burned!
You really saved the day!

376
00:21:30,023 --> 00:21:31,958
