377
00:21:32,058 --> 00:21:33,694
Mhmm...

378
00:21:35,629 --> 00:21:36,597
No good?

379
00:21:36,697 --> 00:21:38,932
That doesn't make me
feel better at all.

380
00:21:39,032 --> 00:21:42,202
Can't you think of something
that would make YOU happy?

381
00:21:42,302 --> 00:21:45,639
Uh... eeeeeeeh?!

382
00:21:49,643 --> 00:21:51,912
[USUI] Huh?
[MISAKI] You...

383
00:21:52,913 --> 00:21:55,415
You did very well today.

384
00:21:57,183 --> 00:21:58,685
Ayuzawa...

385
00:22:03,223 --> 00:22:04,357
[USUI]
So can I ravage you now?

386
00:22:04,457 --> 00:22:05,391
You idiot!

387
00:22:05,491 --> 00:22:07,360
(whining)

388
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:08,829
[KANOU]
Yukimura...

389
00:22:08,929 --> 00:22:11,765
Out of everyone, I really do
respect you most of all.

390
00:22:11,865 --> 00:22:14,467
I can't believe not a
single person noticed
you're really a man.

391
00:22:14,568 --> 00:22:18,238
You've got it wrong, Kanou!
I want to change, but I can't
find my uniform!

392
00:22:18,338 --> 00:22:19,840
[SAKURA]
Sparkly!

393
00:23:49,930 --> 00:23:52,833
[MISAKI]
I'm always so busy, it's a
wonder I'm still awake, huh?

394
00:23:52,933 --> 00:23:55,969
[USUI]
Maybe it'd be best if Kanou
hypnotized you again.

395
00:23:56,069 --> 00:23:57,771
[USUI]
This guy hasn't slept
for nearly a month.

396
00:23:57,871 --> 00:24:00,607
[KANOU]
Very perceptive of you.
Now then, here goes.

397
00:24:00,707 --> 00:24:02,609
[MISAKI]
Hey now! Don't do it, Kanou!

398
00:24:02,709 --> 00:24:04,745
[SUZUNA] Ta‐daa!
[MISAKI] Whoa, Suzuna!

399
00:24:04,845 --> 00:24:07,480
[SUZUNA]
To get right to it, next time
will be a story about summer.

400
00:24:07,581 --> 00:24:11,251
[SATSUKI]
Misa! We're going to the beach
with everyone from Maid Latte!

401
00:24:11,351 --> 00:24:13,386
Does everyone have
their bikinis ready?

402
00:24:13,486 --> 00:24:15,355
